## Next Steps

To complete the Speed Insights setup after deployment:

1. Enable Speed Insights in the Vercel dashboard:
   - Go to your project in Vercel dashboard
   - Navigate to the "Speed Insights" tab
   - Click "Enable" to activate the feature

2. Deploy the application to Vercel:
   - The Speed Insights routes will be available at `/_vercel/speed-insights/*`
   - The tracking script will automatically load at `/_vercel/speed-insights/script.js`

3. View metrics in the dashboard:
   - After deployment and user visits, data will be available in the Speed Insights tab
   - Metrics include Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID, CLS) and other performance indicators

